---
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="phro.design — about" description="About phro.">
  <main class="page">
    <section class="about">
      <div class="media" aria-label="Portrait">
        <!-- Start with a static image. Replace with viewer later. -->
        <img
          src="/previews/about-portrait.png"
          alt="Portrait"
          loading="eager"
          decoding="async"
        />
      </div>

      <div class="copy">
        <p>
          I’m Pietro. I look for the logic in things-grids, particles, forces in
          motion. My work sits at the intersection of creative direction and
          technical build. I don’t just want to design the image; I want to
          engineer the system behind it. I believe most ideas already contain
          their own path forward—the challenge is just seeing the structure
          clearly enough to follow it.
        </p>

        <p>
          phro is a platform for this kind of systems-driven work. It is a
          practice built on restraint and intention. The name is a loose
          phonetic echo of my own, chosen to be intuitive rather than
          descriptive. It’s an open container for work that is precise,
          engineered, and quietly expressive. From Brooklyn to Italy, I build
          things that work as beautifully as they look.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</Layout>

<style>
  .page {
    min-height: 100vh;
    padding: 200px 20px 80px;
    max-width: 960px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    background: #000;
    color: #fff;
  }

  .about {
    display: grid;
    gap: 28px;
    justify-items: center;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .media {
    width: min(520px, 100%);
    aspect-ratio: 1 / 1;
    border-radius: 18px;
    overflow: hidden;
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.03);
  }

  .media img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
    display: block;
    opacity: 0.95;
  }

  .copy {
    width: min(680px, 100%);
    display: grid;
    gap: 14px;
    justify-items: center;
  }

  h1 {
    margin: 0;
    font-family:
      ui-monospace, SFMono-Regular, Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, "Liberation Mono",
      "Courier New", monospace;
    font-size: clamp(22px, 3vw, 34px);
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    text-transform: lowercase;
  }

  p {
    margin: 0;
    max-width: 62ch;
    line-height: 1.7;
    font-size: 14px;
    opacity: 0.8;
  }

  .links {
    display: flex;
    gap: 18px;
    margin-top: 8px;
  }

  .links a {
    color: #fff;
    text-decoration: underline;
    text-underline-offset: 4px;
    text-decoration-thickness: 1px;
    font-family:
      ui-monospace, SFMono-Regular, Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, "Liberation Mono",
      "Courier New", monospace;
    text-transform: lowercase;
    font-size: 13px;
    opacity: 0.9;
  }

  .links a:hover {
    opacity: 1;
  }
</style>
